        EPS_SCF 5.0E-7
        MAX_SCF 10
      &END
    &END SCF
    &XC
      &XC_FUNCTIONAL PBE
      &END XC_FUNCTIONAL
    &END XC
  &END DFT
  &SUBSYS
    &CELL
      ABC 15.0 15.0 15.0
    &END CELL
    &COORD
Ni       8.00000000       8.00000000       7.01741574       28
S       8.00000000       8.00000000       8.98258426       16 
    &END COORD
