      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
      MAGNETIZATION 3
      LEBEDEV_GRID 100
      RADIAL_GRID  250
    &END KIND
    &KIND S
      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
    &END KIND
    &KIND Cl
      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
    &END KIND
    &KIND C
      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
    &END KIND
    &KIND O
      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
    &END KIND
    &KIND F
      BASIS_SET def2-QZVPP
      POTENTIAL ALL
    &END KIND
